@ontos 1.0
@title Ordering fixture
@type conformance
@updated 2026-06-05
@lang en

- Ordered root @id(ordered-root) #beta #alpha
  zeta: Keep this field first.
  alpha: Keep this field second.
  middle:
    - second list item stays first
    - first list item stays second

  - Second child @id(second-child)
    purpose: This child intentionally appears first.

  - First child @id(first-child)
    purpose: This child intentionally appears second.
